		phalange.update(description: '<p>SalveDeus!</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ComoTiaNeivanosrelataemv&aacute;riasaulas,aciviliza&ccedil;&atilde;oMayafoiumadenossasencarna&ccedil;&otilde;es,quandoviemosnapen&iacute;nsuladeYucat&atilde;,noM&eacute;xico,ondet&iacute;nhamosumdesenvolvimentomaterialecient&iacute;ficosuperioraodehoje,comamplocontroledaenergiaat&ocirc;mica.HaviaoHomem-P&aacute;ssaro,quevoavaportodasasdire&ccedil;&otilde;escomummacac&atilde;oespecial,cheiodetubinhosenerg&eacute;ticos.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;EntreosMayas,grandess&aacute;biosrecebiaminstru&ccedil;&otilde;esdiretamentedeCapela,tinhamaVozDiretaerealizavamgrandesfen&ocirc;menos.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AsAmac&ecirc;spassavamsobreascidades,projetandoaenergiadeCapelaparaaquelepovoemantendoaquelas&aacute;reaslivresdeanimaisquenaquela&eacute;pocaaterrorizavamohomem.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;EssasAmac&ecirc;straziamasinstru&ccedil;&otilde;esdosmentores,por&eacute;mnuncaatravessavamoneutr&ocirc;m.Emsuaambi&ccedil;&atilde;o,osMayasdaquelaeradistantetentaramcapturarumadasAmac&ecirc;s.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AtentativadecapturaraquelaAmac&ecirc;produziuadesintegra&ccedil;&atilde;odetodaaquelaciviliza&ccedil;&atilde;o,raz&atilde;opelaqual,at&eacute;osdiasatuais,ahist&oacute;riatradicionaln&atilde;osabeexplicararaz&atilde;odaextin&ccedil;&atilde;odaquelaciviliza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AClarividenten&atilde;odeixouumaHist&oacute;riadetalhadasobreaorigemdaFalangeMission&aacute;riaMaya,por&eacute;m,nopr&oacute;priocantodasMayas,emdiversosacervosescritoseem&aacute;udiodeTiaNeiva,encontramoselementossuficientesparaterumatrajet&oacute;riasobreaHeran&ccedil;aTranscendentaldasMayas.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;NaCartadeTiaNeivaintitulada&ldquo;MayasdeYucat&atilde;&rdquo;,aClarivide