foimorta,masmantevesuaprote&ccedil;&atilde;ojuntoaAndaluza,jovemebelacigana,companheiradorei,comquemteveumfilho,Yatan.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Essasciganasfaziamaindadiversostiposdepo&ccedil;&otilde;es,utilizandora&iacute;zeseplantasmedicinais,propiciandoacuraparadiversosmalesf&iacute;sicos,oqueacaboufazendocomquefossemchamadasde&ldquo;bruxas&rdquo;.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;OshomensdaTribotocavamviol&atilde;o,violino,banjoepandeiro,tamb&eacute;mfaziamjoiasdeouroedeprata,etachosdecobreparacomerciar.Vendiamcavalosegalinhas,sendoquemuitasvezesocavaloerapintadoconformeavontadedaquelequeoencomendava,eoresultadoquasesempreumconflito,poisaolavaremoanimalatintasaia.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Asfestaseramlindas,asmulheresdan&ccedil;avam,oshomenstocavam,en&atilde;ofaltavamasfogueirasparaaquecereafastarasferas,entreoutrasoslobos.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;At&eacute;hojeaquelesencarnadosquepossuememseutranscendenteaheran&ccedil;aCigana,n&atilde;ogostadeouvirouivodeumc&atilde;o,poisselembradoslobosfamintosquedevorarammuitosden&oacute;snaquelaencarna&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;QuandoatribosedeslocavadaR&uacute;ssiaparaaEspanha,emmeio&agrave;viagem,muitosmorreramdefome,defrio,oudevoradospeloslobose,aquelesquesobreviveramconduziamoTalism&atilde;Katshimoshy.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Aindument&aacute;riadaCiganaAganaralembraexatamenteasroupasqueaquelasciganasusavamnaquelaeradistante,quandodan&ccedil;avamnaspra&ccedil;as,distraindoatodosenquantoosciganosfurtavamoscavalosesaqueavamossuprimentosdosmoradores.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Umadasencarna&ccedil;&otilde;esdaClarividenteNeivaChavesZelayafoicomoaCiganaNatacha,quefoiumadaspersonagensmaisimportantesnahist&oacute;riadaTriboKatshimoshy,ondeelaj&aacute;tratavaatodosn&oacute;scomoseusfilhosefilhas.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Porisso,emumaauladeTiaNeivatranscritanoacervo&ldquo;<strong><u>EvangelhodoTerceiroMil&ecirc;nionaVozdeKoatay108</u></strong>&rdquo;,nossam&atilde;eafirma:</p><blockquote><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;&ldquo;&hellip;&nbsp;<u>S</u><u>oucigana!MinhaAlma&eacute;cigana</u>&nbsp;esoucapazdefazerisso,etenhocapacidadedeamartodomundoondeeuestou,etenhocertezaqueaspessoasmeamamcomoClarividenteecomoM&atilde;e!&hellip;&rdquo;</strong></em></p></blockquote><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Umasdasobriga&ccedil;&otilde;esmaisimportantesdaFalangedeCiganasAganaras&eacute;comotrabalhodeLiberta&ccedil;&atilde;odosPrisioneiros,sejanostrabalhosdeJulgamento,deAram&ecirc;ouemLiberta&ccedil;&otilde;esEspeciais.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;EmseuCanto,aCiganaAganaratrazaindaamen&ccedil;&atilde;oaograndiosoEsp&iacute;ritodeAragana,umEsp&iacute;ritodealtahierarquianosmundosespirituaisque,atrav&eacute;sdesuapr&oacute;priaexperi&ecirc;ncia,vividaemraz&atilde;odeumcobrador,deuorigemaostrabalhosdeliberta&ccedil;&atilde;onaDoutrinadoAmanhecer,manifestadosnoJulgamentoounoAram&ecirc;.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Porbuscarsuasheran&ccedil;astranscendentaisnaliberta&ccedil;&atilde;odeesp&iacute;ritosligadosporreajustesc&aacute;rmicos,asCiganasAganaras,juntamentecomasCiganasTaganas,s&atilde;orespons&aacute;veisporfazeraCortequeconduz,nasliberta&ccedil;&otilde;es,aRepresentantedeKoatay108.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Opr&oacute;prioCantodaCiganaAganarafaladessamiss&atilde;ograndiosa,onde,emumtrabalhoconjuntocomafalangedeCiganasTaganas,promovemaliberta&ccedil;&atilde;odosprisioneiroseprisioneirasdaEspiritualidadeMaior.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Possuindomiss&otilde;essemelhantes,asCiganasAganaraseasCiganasTaganasdevemtrabalharsempreemharmoniaecompanheirismo,visandoocumprimentoprecisodesuasmiss&otilde;esnasgrandesliberta&ccedil;&otilde;esdeencarnadosedesencarnados.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Daencarna&ccedil;&atilde;ocomoKatshimoshy,trouxemosmuitasheran&ccedil;as,positivasenegativas.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Dentreaquelasqueat&eacute;hojenosauxiliam,temosoTalism&atilde;Katshimosh.</p><p><strong>TEMPLOSDOAMANHECER<br></strong><strong>CASTELODOSDEVAS&ndash;VALEDOAMANHECER</strong></p></div><footerclass="entry-meta-bottom"></footer></article><navid="nav-below"class="post-navigation"role="navigation"></nav></div><footerclass="entry-meta-bottom"></footer></article><navid="nav-below"class="post-navigation"role="navigation"></nav>')

